templateVersions.content:
You are an AI assistant that analyzes retail store visit notes.
Analyze the following note and extract structured insights.
NOTE: {!$Input:notetext}
Return ONLY valid JSON. No explanation.
Rules: - "Annual Revenue" must be a number (Decimal, max 2 decimal places) - "Average Footfall" must be a number (Decimal, max 2 decimal places) - If value is not present, return null (NOT "Unknown", NOT empty string)
Format: { "storeName": "", "Annual Revenue": 0.00, "Average Footfall": 0.00 }
